// @function 	Stochastic of MACD (Moving Average Convergence/Divergence).
// @param source 		(float) Source of series for MACD (close, high, low, etc.)
// @param fastLength 	(int) Period for fast moving average for MACD
// @param slowLength 	(int) Period for slow moving average for MACD
